Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他乘客呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都下车了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下车…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(化猫)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的月光照着你徘徊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话却说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹记那虚伪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却那温暖的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有如失了魂的空虚眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的下弦月隐脏在云间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述说着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚只能够幽幽叹息吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(大结局)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列车是不会停的，除非…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直待在这…\N不要！我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想点办法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定办得到吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想替后辈报仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…想替节子小姐报仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！帮那个被杀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市…川…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森…谷…先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过份的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫呈现出来的吗？\N看着吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻划在现场的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从记忆中得到“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”则唤出因果与渊源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你不好~\N“形”、“真”与“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃至转生之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请您让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”之景象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说福田市长贪污！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(每朝日报)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经掌握到报导的题材了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森谷…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的掌握到内幕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市长先生\N频频与铁路公司的董事见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是掌握到非常可靠的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这种时候面谈\N不好意思，市川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看也知道不对劲吧\N我们可不是什么三流的周刊杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能只凭这点情报\N就刊登你的报导
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上虽然这么说\N其实你是在忌妒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忌妒？你说谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是说森谷先生…忌妒我罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我爆出顶级的料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的爆料啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么忌妒啊眼红什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人才会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来派你去跑新闻是一大失败呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白忙一场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去报家庭版吧\N我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对会让它变独家的\N别搞错了，市川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样根本没有身为记者的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(吉祥料亭)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女色狼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间…逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…\N小心走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们单独谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还不能上报吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如我所料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你一定办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我对你说了那么严厉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我吧！市川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我对那家伙很赏识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才对她特别严厉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么时候的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片都是你自已拍的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底片呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，到外面去谈吧\N咦，可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…可是独家啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该不想让别人知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是报社里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(康康咖啡厅)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是市长与东都电铁的董事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是日本桥建设的社长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点都是在吉祥料亭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市长为了替东都电铁\N大开便利之门而通过条例
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该收了不少贿赂当作回报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪家银行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市井银行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市长的叔叔曾是那里的总经理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已经掌握那么多的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就把这件事报导出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交稿的时间是明天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天用头版的方式刊登
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没什么时间，你办得到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报导…由我全权负责？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这新闻是你自已跑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是由你执笔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前误会森谷先生您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为您一直觉得我是个\N轻浮又没用的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为我不可能\N跑出什么像样的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来\N我也能成为第一线的新闻记者了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道“此方旅馆”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那里写稿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我闭关写稿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这篇报导千万别让任何人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排版也由我亲自做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我是上次打电话来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有点事情想跟您谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不算是什么好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，刻意到其他地方见面\N可能不太妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会亲自登门拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”  …越来越接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，你说可以让我\N在电影里出现是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托嘛，我很想出名啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说~什么\N也不要在这里窝一辈子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(市政府)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你那儿的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚可是让我尝到睽违许久…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓破胆的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(此方旅馆)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好，这里是此方旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(开什么玩笑，那个臭老太婆)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一天到晚照顾老人\N我哪受得了啊…)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(因为有那个人)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我才有勇气活下去)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(节子  真讨厌真讨厌)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一辈子过着抬不起头的生活)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够悲哀…的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那种丧家之犬不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是个新闻记者呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我是市川…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(康康咖啡厅)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(千代)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人问过我要不要当歌手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，当时…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会拒绝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森谷先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有被人跟踪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…你是怎么了森谷先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么抖成那样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个题材\N可是很厉害的独家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会\N又没有人会追杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是替那家伙着想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给她一点忠告而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么性急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要在这地方看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？\N(森谷这原稿不能见人)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这新闻不能登\N为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(把它烧了)\N这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正男！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正男，快起床！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森谷先生，你太过份了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这根本就是越权！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟上头报告！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的，我已经跟上头报告过了\N你骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从一开始就打算这么做对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始你就想抢走我的原稿\N无药可救…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真卑鄙！骗子！\N真是没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就打算那么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去找她谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么谈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛！我要跟社长说！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着被解雇吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事多少会带来点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正交给你处理就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嫉妒你？\N可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑死人！\N可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会在意那种小事呢\N可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不过是个女人\N可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻脑筋就死板板的\N可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只是把眼光…放得比较远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让开通典礼蒙上任何阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一不小心就会变成丑闻的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你跟福田市长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…\N你说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…\N女人就是见识浅短啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不会看情势做事呢\N原来从一开始你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打算报导那则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后只要你肯乖乖听我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把新闻送到其他报社去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手上还有其他证据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正笨的人是你哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在这时候\N我才觉得自已活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民不会原谅你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你消失就没问题了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手住手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个臭老太婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不快点死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是个笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还想给她忠告呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却自已…\N自已找死？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意气风发的女记者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为梦想破灭而自杀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛，好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体动弹不得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开…开什么玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看到我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这怠忽职守的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快发现我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你…饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这连小篇幅的报导都排不上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想当女明星…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的酬劳…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯这是自杀，是自杀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在于宇宙之间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类存在于世上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要幻化为物怪之形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须依附人类的因果与渊源\N而形成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然一旦出现于世间之物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就非斩不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此处已成为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化猫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故需…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解.放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗？\N市民也对此翘首以盼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望二期工程能够尽快进行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白日梦吗？一点也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，市川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别恨我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了…你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你不在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法笑得开怀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在随处可见的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些无可取代的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能够好好珍惜地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已经别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随风缓缓飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在那早已看不见的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N也令人珍爱到无可比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生于世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪亦生于世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦妖怪与人之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”与“理”相呼应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便可得到“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得其形
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将幻化成不得存于世上的物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪无法根绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却可斩除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故而退魔剑存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剑之人亦存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的“真”与“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请仔细道来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪尚存于人世之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到会发生\N这么不可思议的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…来了~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(谢谢观赏)
